況愈下，睇見佢地寫既野，嘩眾取寵就得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"前線記者夠勇武<br />\n但係佢地有部份對自己記者呢個身份同操守好執著<br />\n所以學伍公子話，公民記應該先係公民後係記者，要盡咗公民義務先再盡記者操守，對家成日話黃媒黑記，問題就係在於有黃媒但無乜黑記，真正幫到我地既係佢地所謂既「黑記」。<br />\n<br />\n而記者之上有編輯，就係控制咩新聞出到街咩新聞出唔到街，所以你寫支持港獨既評論係唔會係立場蘋果呢啲黃媒度登出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再講啲傳媒高層成日同中聯辦既人飲飲食食，分分中收晒錢，事頭婆聖誕演辭有香港人係側邊奏樂，唔報；授勳名單有幾位同香港有關係既人，唔報。咁樣既質素其實好難叫人撐。"},{"pid":"fb855141ab5fef2436419b131ed77ebc52b7bcc8","tid":2009751,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大紀元<br />\nHK Free Press<br />\n沒蘋果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>同意<br />\n黎智英第一個衝出嚟捉本土派同獨派鬼<br />\n理大一役記者爆手足逃生路線<br />\n係呢排查陶輝夠勇武，所以要課金係應該直接課俾果兩個記者<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">呢間公司係維護佢自己既新聞自由但係打壓同陣營小數派既發言權，係集體主義反民主既支持者</span></ins><br />\n所以真係唔應該有蘋果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n置頂唔該<br />\n<br />\n大紀元<br />\n（大紀元美國版 全英文 係幾高質，可以上網睇下大紀元－美國思想領袖 巴絲英文好 就直接睇英文，英文唔好就睇中文)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_78IIcKAIDpp6SJOlf3vDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC_78IIcKAIDpp6SJOlf3vDA&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=8af1cffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_78IIcKAIDpp6SJOlf3vDA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmWhuFRkZKu0g-e1xrlakVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCmWhuFRkZKu0g-e1xrlakVA&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=1e7e11fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmWhuFRkZKu0g-e1xrlakVA</a><br />\nHK Free Press<br />\n加埋maddog daily<br />\n<br />\n沒蘋果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會支持蘋果 蘋果日報背後就係反侵既金主 加上經常打壓本土派同其他少數既媒體！<br />\n一定唔支持"},{"pid":"e67149923d9634777ba8de614c4cbd63af709936","tid":2009751,"uid":88134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d2e8c4e23240ea5b1f4c05f8e5c3302b4b80af3","tid":2009751,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"大紀元<br />\nHK Free Press<br />\n沒蘋果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"講漏咗<br />\n呢間公司既大方向其實就係迎合香港人睇人仆街最開心既心態<br />\n姐係政治娛樂化既其中一個推手<br />\n有份搞到香港人淨係識得恥笑對家低手<br />\n如果有一日香港變美麗新世界，香港人因為娛樂至死，呢間野係應該收皮"},{"pid":"6e9c837e56fef5588985bb385fa0dad79e3c8033","tid":2009751,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67149923d9634777ba8de614c4cbd63af709936","tid":2009751,"uid":88134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d2e8c4e23240ea5b1f4c05f8e5c3302b4b80af3","tid":2009751,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"大紀元<br />\nHK Free Press<br />\n沒蘋果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"講漏咗<br />\n呢間公司既大方向其實就係迎合香港人睇人仆街最開心既心態<br />\n姐係政治娛樂化既其中一個推手<br />\n有份搞到香港人淨係識得恥笑對家低手<br />\n如果有一日香港變美麗新世界，香港人因為娛樂至死，呢間野係應該收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蘋果真係不了，基本既傳媒底線 同責任都沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9971d5e604463b226ca1d08d3a8ba08eed7686c1","tid":2009751,"uid":88134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e9c837e56fef5588985bb385fa0dad79e3c8033","tid":2009751,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo